[Guest]: here actually Bangalore has nothing you know that kind of a thing gulabi nagara lobby nagara

01:28:09.040 --> 01:28:14.240
[Guest]: you know that kind of a pun used to used I mean garden city right gulabi nagara and things

01:28:14.240 --> 01:28:21.080
[Guest]: like that so he was there so there were different groups you know across Karnataka so all these

01:28:21.080 --> 01:28:25.800
[Guest]: groups played different kinds of roles and put different kinds of pressures and brought

01:28:25.800 --> 01:28:32.400
[Guest]: in different kinds of ideas during the unification of Karnataka itself so they all the all you

