[Guest]: they said please explain to a European audience as to why a film star is being kidnapped in

02:05:00.640 --> 02:05:06.040
[Guest]: the first place and why is why is it such a big issue and why is the state shut down

02:05:06.040 --> 02:05:10.720
[Guest]: because a film star has been kidnapped and why is the state government negotiating why

02:05:10.720 --> 02:05:14.600
[Guest]: are the state agencies getting involved in this whole thing then I had to tell them that

02:05:14.600 --> 02:05:21.600
[Guest]: this person called Rajkumar is not an actor he's a cultural icon and he was such a powerful

02:05:21.600 --> 02:05:28.400
[Guest]: guy that in 1954 I think he's made his debut in Kannada and then his the reunification

02:05:28.400 --> 02:05:33.520
[Guest]: movement was happening at the same time and you know how they identified the outer reaches

02:05:33.520 --> 02:05:43.440
