[Guest]: all his speeches he says why are you giving me this doctoral degree I am a I am not very

02:06:15.440 --> 02:06:20.840
[Guest]: educated all that but then to explain all this to a Western audience was a fantastic

02:06:20.840 --> 02:06:28.120
