02:07:23.840 --> 02:07:31.440
[Amit Varma]: languages and all and it is absolutely anti-national to then impose upon that this monolithic vision

02:07:31.440 --> 02:07:36.520
[Amit Varma]: that this is nationalism only this one thing and try to sub I mean in a sense it's it's

