02:39:37.160 --> 02:39:44.640
[Guest]: the same agenda so so that homogenization thing is part it's it's it's there in the

02:39:44.640 --> 02:39:49.920
[Guest]: it's embedded in the idea of the nation state itself so you think you have to think through

02:39:49.920 --> 02:39:56.200
[Guest]: those terms otherwise it doesn't make sense but what happened why there is this kind of

02:39:56.200 --> 02:40:03.400
[Guest]: counter thing that has happened is because the borders became irrelevant economic borders

02:40:03.400 --> 02:40:08.880
[Guest]: became irrelevant and and and you know I mean this migration became such a big phenomena

02:40:08.880 --> 02:40:14.160
[Guest]: and every Indian family now has seems to have traveled right so all that started getting

