[Guest]: dismantled so the whole if at all I write a next I mean I'm writing two other books

02:40:19.560 --> 02:40:23.480
[Guest]: but then the big book that I want to write is about the decline of the linguistic state

02:40:23.480 --> 02:40:29.000
[Guest]: Wow right so the whole your how did you premise your idea of linguistic state when it was

02:40:29.000 --> 02:40:34.240
[Guest]: conceived in the 20s and the Congress passed a resolution all of that happened you conceived

02:40:34.240 --> 02:40:39.960
[Guest]: of it as a sealed border which had this language this language this language you thought of

02:40:39.960 --> 02:40:45.000
[Guest]: it as the imagination itself was faulty you never thought there would come a time when

02:40:45.000 --> 02:40:49.320
